   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Backpropagation Through Time (BPTT)\n",
    "\n",
    "Training objective:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{\\partial \\mathscr L}{\\partial \\mathbf W_h} =\\sum_{t=1}^{T}\\frac{\\partial \\mathscr L}{\\partial \\mathbf h_t}\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf h_t}{\\partial \\mathbf W_h}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "But:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf h_t}{\\partial \\mathbf h_{t-k}}=\\prod_{i=t-k+1}^{t}\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf h_i}{\\partial \\mathbf h_{i-1}}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "with:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf h_i}{\\partial \\mathbf h_{i-1}}\n",
    "=\\mathbf W_h \\cdot \\text{diag}(\\sigma'(\\mathbf z_t))\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Repeated matrix multiplication → instability.\n",
    "\n",
    "## The Vanishing Gradient Problem\n",
    "\n",
    "Simplified Recurrence\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf h_t = \\sigma(\\mathbf W_h \\mathbf h_{t-1})\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Derivative:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf h_t}{\\partial \\mathbf h_{t-1}}\n",
    "=\n",
    "\\mathbf W_h \\cdot \\text{diag}(\\sigma'(\\mathbf z))\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Repeated products:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\prod_{i=1}^{k} \\mathbf W_h \\boldsymbol{\\lambda}_i\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    ":::{.columns}\n",
    "\n",
    "::::{.column width=\"50%\"}\n",
    "If:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\rho(\\mathbf W_h) < 1\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    ">Gradient vanishes.\n",
    "\n",
    "::::\n",
    "\n",
    "::::{.column width=\"50%\"}\n",
    "\n",
    "If:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\rho(\\mathbf W_h) > 1\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    ">Exploding gradient.\n",
    "\n",
    "::::\n",
    "\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "# Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM)\n",
    "\n",
    "## LSTM Gate Equations\n",
    "\n",
    ":::{.callout-note}\n",
    "Allow constant error flow through a memory cell.\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "**Forget gate:**\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf f_t = \\sigma\\left(\\mathbf W_f [\\mathbf h_{t-1} \\, \\mathbf x_t] + \\mathbf b_f\\right)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Input gate:**\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf i_t = \\sigma\\left(\\mathbf W_i [\\mathbf h_{t-1} \\, \\mathbf x_t] + \\mathbf b_i\\right)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "**Output:**\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf o_t = \\sigma\\left(\\mathbf W_o [\\mathbf h_{t-1} \\, \\mathbf x_t] + \\mathbf b_o\\right)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Input Node**\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\widetilde{\\mathbf c} = \\tanh\\left(\\mathbf W_c [\\mathbf h_{t-1} \\, \\mathbf x_t] + \\mathbf b_c\\right)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "![LSTM Cell Update with Input](/images/lstm-1.svg){width=70%}\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Cell update\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf c_t = \\mathbf f_t \\odot \\mathbf c_{t-1} + \\mathbf i_t \\odot \\widetilde{\\mathbf c}_t\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf h_t = \\mathbf o_t \\odot \\tanh(\\mathbf c_t)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "![LSTM cell](/images/lstm-3.svg)\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Why LSTM Works\n",
    "\n",
    "If:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf f_t \\approx 1\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Then:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf c_t}{\\partial \\mathbf c_{t-1}} \\approx 1\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    ">Gradient preserved.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Tensorflow: LSTM"
   ]
  },
